WEBVTT

00:02:56.708 --> 00:03:01.855
which requires skill, financing,
local and global partnerships,

00:03:01.855 --> 00:03:04.525
and extraordinary perseverance.

00:03:04.525 --> 00:03:06.610
But why pan-African?

00:03:07.590 --> 00:03:12.188
The scramble for Africa
during the Berlin Conference of 1884 --

00:03:12.188 --> 00:03:16.924
where, quite frankly, we Africans
were not exactly consulted --

00:03:16.924 --> 00:03:22.332
(Laughter) (Applause) --

00:03:23.542 --> 00:03:26.003
resulted in massive fragmentation

00:03:26.003 --> 00:03:28.534
and many sovereign states
with small populations:

00:03:28.534 --> 00:03:31.576
Liberia, four million;
Cape Verde, 500,000.